          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The threshold  of (g,n+p) reaction is 12.5 MeV so the",
                " cross section measured is really the  sum  of  cross",
                " sections of (g,n) and (g,n+p) reactions."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
